skype - change settings so it works with camera, choose microphone in ubuntu sound settings at top.

make python automatically start in idle - it will depend on the version of idle
gedit ~/.local/share/applications/mimeapps.list
Search for text/x-python, and make sure it is like this:
text/x-python=idle-python2.7.desktop


play native flash files in chrome:
Edit /usr/share/mime/packages/freedesktop.org.xml file and change
<mime-type type="application/vnd.adobe.flash.movie">
to
<mime-type type="application/x-shockwave-flash">
and then run
sudo update-mime-database /usr/share/mime


If chrome does not search automatically, go to settings->search->manage search engines, and make a new search engine with "https://www.google.com.au/search?q=%s" as the key.



